image. Oh, for language </div><div class="t m8b0 x58 he y4bf ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to express the glory of the bright world to </div><div class="t m385 x58 he ya38 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">come ! I thirst for the living streams that </div><div class="t m78a x58 he y173 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">make glad the city of our </div><div class="t m14a1 xc7 h21 y349 ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God.&quot;—Early </div><div class="t m1739 x58 h21 y4e ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Writings, </div><div class="t m1350 x23 he y4e ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page 39. </div><div class="t m87a xbc he y60e ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Language is altogether too feeble to at-</div><div class="t maf7 x58 he ycc1 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tempt a description of heaven. As the scene </div><div class="t m51e x58 he y1072 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rises before me, I am lost in amazement. </div><div class="t md25 x58 he y6e9 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Carried away with the surpassing splendor </div><div class="t m1138 x58 he y319 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and excellent glory, I lay down the pen, and </div><div class="t m642 x58 he y1b9 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">exclaim, &apos;Oh, what love ! what wondrous </div><div class="t meaa x58 he y584 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">love!&apos; The most exalted language fails to </div><div class="t m625 x58 he y6df ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">describe the glory of heaven or the match-</div><div class="t mad2 x58 he y100 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">less depths of a Saviour&apos;s </div><div class="t maf2 xcd h21 y604 ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">love.&quot;--Ibid., </div><div class="t ma07 x1de he y604 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. </div><div class="t m2fe6 x1c he y2ff ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">289. </div><div class="t me9e x56 he ya5f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. Where in heaven is God&apos;s throne </div><div class="t m6f6 x58 he yab5 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">located ? Ps. 11:4; 102:19; Rev. 11:19. </div><div class="t m143c x55 h33 y2006 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Introduction </div><